tc.compiler.tree.visit

Class Dump

  • java.lang.Object
    • tc.compiler.tree.visit.TreeVisitorBase<Void>
      • tc.compiler.tree.visit.Dump
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeVisitor<Void>

    public final class Dump
extends TreeVisitorBase<Void>
    Dump an AST to a stream. Uses prefix order with indentation.

    Using Void for the type parameter because there is no return type.
